{{Infobox sport governing body |name = Andorran Cycling Federation |abbrev = FAC |logo = Federació Andorrana de Ciclisme Logo.png |logosize = 150px |sport = [[Bicycle racing]] |jurisdiction = National |aff = [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] |headquarters = [[Ordino]], [[Andorra]] |url = http://www.faciclisme.com/ |countryflag = Andorra }}
The '''Andorran Cycling Federation''' or '''FAC''' (in [[Catalan language|Catalan]]: ''Federació Andorrana de Ciclisme'') is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Andorra]].
The FMC is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and the [[Union Européenne de Cyclisme|UEC]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.faciclisme.com/la-federacio|title=Federació Andorrana de Ciclisme|author=Govern d'Andorra|work=faciclisme.com}}</ref>
