{{ref improve|date=March 2013}} {{Infobox prepared food | name = Ciorbă de perișoare | image = Ciorbă cu perișoare.jpg | image_size = | caption = | alternate_name = | country = [[Romania]] | region = | creator = | course = | type = [[Sour soup]] | served = | main_ingredient = [[Meatball]]s (minced [[pork]]), [[rice]], [[spice]]s, [[ciorbă]] | variations = Sulu köfte | calories = | other = }}
'''Ciorbă de perișoare'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dexonline.ro/definitie/peri%C8%99oar%C4%83|title=Definition of perișoáră|publisher=DEX on line|language=ro}}</ref> is a [[Romania]]n traditional [[sour soup]] with [[meatball]]s. Perișoare are meatballs usually made with minced pork meat, mixed with [[rice]] and [[spice]]s and boiled in a [[ciorbă]].
