{{italic title}}
'''''Festival dalmatinskih klapa Omiš''''' (Croatian for Omiš Festival of Dalmatian Klapa) is a [[music festival]] of [[klapa]] singing held annually in [[Omiš]], [[Croatia]]. It has existed since 1966,<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jutarnji.hr/40-godina-omiskog-festivala--dalmacija-nije-samo-serenada/163832/ |language=Croatian |newspaper=[[Jutarnji list]] |title=40 godina omiškog Festivala: Dalmacija nije samo serenada |date=26 November 2006 |accessdate=18 December 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219015141/http://www.jutarnji.hr/40-godina-omiskog-festivala--dalmacija-nije-samo-serenada/163832/ |archivedate=19 December 2013 |df= }}</ref> and it is the most important klapa event.<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.vecernji.hr/glazba/cesarice-slave-dvadeseti-rodendan-u-lisinskom-905849 | language = Croatian | newspaper = [[Večernji list]] | title = Cesarice slave dvadeseti rođendan u Lisinskom | date = 30 November 2013 | accessdate = 2013-12-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.slobodnadalmacija.hr/Kultura/tabid/81/articleType/ArticleView/articleId/129421/Default.aspx | language = Croatian | newspaper = [[Slobodna Dalmacija]] | title = Nikola Buble: ‘Kaštela’ su zabava, a ’Omiš’ gubi snagu | date = 14 February 2011 | accessdate = 18 December 2013}}</ref>

