{{Infobox language family |name=Lunda |ethnicity= |region= |familycolor=Niger-Congo |fam2=[[Atlantic–Congo]] |fam3=[[Benue–Congo]] |fam4=[[Southern Bantoid]] |fam5=[[Bantu languages|Bantu]] ([[Guthrie classification of Bantu languages#Zone L|Zone L.50]]) |glotto=ruun1239 |glottorefname= Ruund–Salampasu }}
