{{Infobox Union |name= Fagforbundet |country= [[Norway]] |affiliation= [[Norwegian Confederation of Trade Unions|LO]] |members= c. 364 000 |full_name= Norwegian Union of Municipal and General Employees |native_name= Fagforbundet |image= [[File:Fagforbundet logo.png|150px]] |founded= |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Oslo]], Norway |people= [[Mette Nord]] |website= [http://www.fagforbundet.no www.fagforbundet.no] |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''Norwegian Union of Municipal and General Employees''' ({{lang-no|Fagforbundet}}) is a [[trade union]] in [[Norway]]. It has a membership of 364,000 and is affiliated with the [[Norwegian Confederation of Trade Unions]] (LO).
It was founded in 2003 as a merger of the [[Norwegian Union of Municipal Employees]] and the [[Norwegian Association of Health and Social Care Personnel]]
