{{Infobox country telephone plan | country = San Marino | country_link = San Marino | continent = Europe | country_calling_code = +378 | international_prefix = 00 | trunk_prefix = +387 6651474 }}
'''Telephone numbers in San Marino''' are 6 to 10 digits long. Numbers starting with either ''0'', ''8'' or ''9'' are assigned to landlines, ''6'' is used for mobile services, ''5'' for IP telephony services and ''7'' for premium numbers. There's no trunk code: all the digits are always dialed.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.itu.int/dms_pub/itu-t/oth/02/02/T02020000B50001PDFE.pdf |title=National Numbering Plans : San Marino|website=[[ITU]]|access-date=1 April 2017|language=English}}</ref>
The [[List of country calling codes|country code]] for [[San Marino]] is ''378'',<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.itu.int/itudoc/itu-t/ob-lists/icc/e164_763.pdf |title=List of ITU-T recommendation E.164 - assigned country codes |publisher=[[International Telecommunication Union]] |format=PDF |access-date=1 April 2017 |page=5}}</ref> but landlines are reachable via the Italian country code ''39'' as well. The [[international call prefix]] is 00. The emergency numbers are "112"/"113" (police), "115" (fire) and "118" (medical).<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.itu.int/net/itu-t/inrdb/e129_important_numbers.aspx?country=87 |title=International Numbering Resources Database - San Marino |publisher=[[International Telecommunication Union]] |access-date=1 April 2017}}</ref>
== History ==
Until 1996, San Marino was part of the [[Telephone numbers in Italy|Italian telephone numbering plan]], using the Italian area code "0549", but in that year it adopted its own country code "378". However dialing arrangements between San Marino and Italy continued as before. In 1998, as Italy switched to a [[Closed telephone numbering plan|closed dialling plan]], San Marino incorporated the 0549 area code into its subscribers' numbers.
The following numbers are equivalent: * "0549 xxx xxx": from Italy * "+378 xxx xxx": from rest of the world * "+39 0549 xxx xxx": from rest of the world, using the Italian country code * "+378 0549 xxx xxx": from rest of the world, using the San Marino country code and the Italian area code
==See also== *[[Telephone numbers in Italy]] *[[Telephone numbers in Vatican City]]
